Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.82,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Things were busy that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:13.28,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Perhaps due to all those frequent disasters last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.33,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Curses were springing up like maggots.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:47.86,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Exorcise. Consume.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.32,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:55.12,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Exorcise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:56.54,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,80)}Consume.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:00:59.50,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It's a taste nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:01.58,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,The taste of a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:07.80,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Like swallowing a rag used to wipe up shit and vomit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:09.59,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Exorcise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:11.84,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Consume.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:16.10,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,What I witnessed was nothing out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:17.97,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,A hideous evil known to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:24.44,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Despite knowing that, I still chose to be\N a sorcerer who saves others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:30.03,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,That's what I've been telling myself ever since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:32.36,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Ever since that day.
Comment: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:33.53,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.33,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,This building
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.71,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,belonged to the president of a company that ran\N a chain of barbecue restaurants in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:52.01,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,However, his business suffered a devastating blow\N due to the mad cow disease outbreak last July.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:55.51,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Burdened by huge debts,\N he committed suicide with his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:59.35,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Since then, the mansion has become\N a well-known haunted location.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:04.19,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,From local school kids to college students\N from outside, and even part-timers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:08.36,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,many visit it as a test of courage,\N and many of them go missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.53,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,As rumors continued to multiply,\Nthe damage must have kept on escalating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:18.87,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Rumors around haunted locations and such\N do tend to spread rather quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:25.38,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable how fast word gets around\N these days thanks to the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:30.13,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,All this just means more work for us sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.68,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Additionally, three elementary school kids\N went missing on their way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:40.35,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Their friends, families, or the police\Nmust be out looking for them. {ah yes, colleagues of elementary school kids}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:45.52,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,If they get to the mansion, there's a good chance\N they might end up as victims themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:49.48,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,We have to sever the root\N of the problem as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:55.20,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,HQ seems to have the same idea.\NThat's why they sent me along to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.37,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,It must be important\Nif they're willing to pay {\i1}my{\i0} fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.41,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Are you extorting them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.04,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,You make it sound so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:06.17,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,It's called negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.08,Default,Assistant Supervisor,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.84,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Let's go, then. {LET'S FUCKING GOOOOOOOOOOOOO}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:18.68,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Emerge from the darkness that is darker than black.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:19.80,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Purify that which{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.47,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,A Veil won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.18,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.81,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,I don't sense the presence of any curses here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:30.52,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,There's a very good chance that\N it's inside the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:35.28,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,You can cast the Veil later \Nif we end up attacking it from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.20,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,It's unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.49,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Seems like something's blocking the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.46,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.59,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Mei{*Mei-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:54.84,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.76,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Its presence is all around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.22,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.94,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,I don't need that, but I'm guessing you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.27,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.44,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.96,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,{\an8}This place is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.71,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Oh, it still has electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:37.63,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Let's take a quick look around the building first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.76,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,I'll take this floor. You take the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.26,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Huh? All by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.31,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Is there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:48.39,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,N-No, i-it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.39,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Off you go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.15,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.03,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.62,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,You could be the next big Scream Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:37.04,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Jeez! Please don't startle me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.13,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,You got startled all on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:43.84,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Are you done exploring the first floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.51,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,This is the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.93,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:54.31,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,I was walking down the first floor hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:56.65,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:02.44,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,I know I entered a room at the end of the hallway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.49,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Boxes of snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.62,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Bags of chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:08.66,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Juice cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.49,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.16,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Sweatshirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.04,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,I've seen these three times by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:21.92,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Did you notice these marks?\N I made them on my way through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:28.18,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,It would seem that we're \Nalready inside the belly of the beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.10,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.52,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:43.65,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,How long {\i1}is{\i0} this hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:49.07,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,We've been moving for thirty minutes, so about four kilometers so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:53.04,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,It's not an innate domain, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:54.79,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.08,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Those are manifestations of one's mindscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.00,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Any other ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.84,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,This must be a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.46,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:09.22,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,The victims were most likely trapped here too,\Nand eventually killed by the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:17.14,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Considering it's using techniques like this,\Nthe curse itself should be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:21.02,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,If we can just escape this barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.74,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Time for a quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:29.11,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,How would you break this, Utahime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.87,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,This hallway is repeating itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.71,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,At first...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:42.84,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,I thought it was like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.17,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Bold of you to touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.92,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,I assumed it was shaped like a donut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:52.01,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,But we passed by four of the marks you made, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.68,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,When I counted how many steps apart they were, I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.77,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,122,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.23,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,203,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.39,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,157,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.69,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,and 270 steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:05.02,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,So the spacing between marks was random.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.94,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.90,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,The interval between repetitions isn't consistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:14.70,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,So I think... it must be something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.83,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,The barrier is patching spaces together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:23.38,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,I think if we both run down the hallway\N at top speed, then at some point...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.51,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,It'll break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.38,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Close. Ninety points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.39,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,D'oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.64,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,What did I miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:41.52,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Don't you think it would be more effective\N if we ran in opposite directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:43.06,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.23,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,If my patching theory is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:51.20,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,running in opposite directions would make it harder\N for the curse to hold the barrier together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.20,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Once we have an opening, we might be able to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.45,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,One hundred points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:56.83,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,It's settled, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:01.66,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,If this works, I'll be expecting a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.67,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,How much do you have in savings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.46,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.71,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Never mind. I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:09.80,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:11.72,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.93,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.18,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.69,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.02,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Wait, wha{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:49.04,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,I'm here to save your ass, Utahime.
Comment: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:49.09,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:19.01,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.30,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,You cryin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.22,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.52,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Respect your seniors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.18,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,If I was crying, would you console me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.27,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,I would certainly appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.02,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Nah, I know you wouldn't cry, {*}Miss Mei{*Mei-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.02,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.36,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.03,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Gojo! You listen here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:40.45,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,I don't need your hel{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.04,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Don't swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.37,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I'll consume it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.96,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Satoru, it's not nice to pick on the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.17,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,What kinda idiot picks on the strong? {Who the fuck would pick on someone strong?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:59.55,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,You're the one who is picking on her, Geto{**-kun}.\N You don't even know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.39,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.93,Default,Shoko,0,0,0,,Utahime{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.35,Default,Shoko,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.60,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:10.73,Default,Shoko,0,0,0,,We hadn't heard from you for two whole days. I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:13.73,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:18.32,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,Shoko! Don't turn out like those two, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.78,Default,Shoko,0,0,0,,No way I'll become trash like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.87,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Look at the trash where Utahime just walked by!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.54,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.25,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait, two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:34.42,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah, was it one of those barriers\N that messes with your perception of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.84,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\an8}They're rare, but they do pop up\N every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.67,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\an8}The whole situation did seem odd \Nsince {*}Miss Mei{*Mei-san} was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.59,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,{\an8}That seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.84,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:48.18,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, I just realized that I technically worked for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:52.77,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,{\an8}Maybe I should ask for additional compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.27,Default,Utahime,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's planning another extortion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.27,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,{\an8}Back to the topic, you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.28,Default,Mei Mei,0,0,0,,Where is the Veil?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.28,0:14:06.20,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next up is the explosion that occurred yesterday\N in Hamamatsu, Shizuoka.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.74,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}The explosion was caused due to degradation of gas pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.16,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Our reporter on the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:12.58,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,One of you told the assistant supervisor that you'd\N cast the Veil yourself and left them behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.13,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,And then you forgot to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.46,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.00,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\an8}{*}Teach{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.88,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're better than pointing fingers at each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.01,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,So it was you, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:29.06,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Is a Veil even necessary in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:32.73,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Does it even matter if normies see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:35.44,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,It's not like they can see curses or\N cursed techniques, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.19,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Of course it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:45.45,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,The primary factor preventing an outbreak\N of curses is the citizens' peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:51.95,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,That's why we have to conceal the\N threats they can't see as far as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.25,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,And that's not all{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.79,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:04.97,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Looking out for the weak is a pain in the ass, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:05.18,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}Looking out for the weak is a pain in the ass, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:05.63,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Looking out for the weak is a pain in the ass, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.10,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Survival of the weakest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.89,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,That's the ideal form society should take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.56,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Help the weak and keep the strong in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.19,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:18.73,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Sorcerers exist to protect non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:24.74,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Is that your moral argument? I hate moral arguments. {i do think "moral argument" is better but i'll stick to the line we used in the movie for consistency} {fuck that i'll just update the movie}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.16,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:32.95,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Assigning responsibilities to the strong\N in the name of some cause is what weak people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:46.26,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Get off your high horse and\N quit spouting that feel-good bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.39,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Blegh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.80,Default,Shoko,0,0,0,,I'm outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:49.85,Default,Shoko,0,0,0,,{\pos(1007,1020)}I'm outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:49.89,Default,Shoko,0,0,0,,{\pos(1041.44,984.09)\fscx101.66\fscy101.66\bord3.66\shad1.83}I'm outta here.
