Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:53.47,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Why don't we take this outside, Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.60,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,You feeling lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.89,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.11,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep fooling around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.28,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,And where's Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:04.74,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:05.78,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Maybe the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:07.91,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.62,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,I'm going to have you two go on a mission together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.49,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,What's with the faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.12,Default,Both,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1020)}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.12,Default,Both,0,0,0,,{\pos(1200,1020)}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.92,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,I honestly think it's too important \Nto be assigned to you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.96,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,but {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama} asked for you specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.80,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Your mission has two goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:29.22,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,{*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama} has found a compatible Star Plasma Vessel. {geto explains it later}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:33.26,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,You are to escort that girl and erase her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.27,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Escort a brat and erase her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.35,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.06,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Has he finally gone senile?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:44.52,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It's spring. He'll become the principal soon.\N It must be getting to his head. {spring is when new school year starts}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.03,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Jokes aside, though{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:49.11,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll be the one to decide if I let that off as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.57,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Is this about resetting {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama}'s technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:52.95,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.54,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:02.92,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,{*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama} has the technique of Immortality,\N but that doesn't grant him eternal youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.71,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be an issue if all he did was get older,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:10.80,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,but after he ages to a certain point,\N the technique will begin to rewrite his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:13.76,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.02,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,He'll cease to be human and\N become a higher form of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:20.81,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that? Sounds cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:26.78,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,According to {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama}, \Nthose who reach that state of being have no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:29.78,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It means {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama} \Nwould cease to be {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:36.45,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,The jujutsu schools, the pillars of jujutsu society,\N and the many barrier techniques of assistant supervisors
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:41.04,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,are all being strengthened by {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:46.67,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Without the aid of his power, we could \Nhardly maintain security or clean up after missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:51.63,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,In the worst-case scenario, \N{*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama} could even become a threat to mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.68,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,That's why, every five hundred years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:58.43,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,he finds the Star Plasma Vessel{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}someone \Nwho is compatible with him{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}and assimilates them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.52,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,overwriting his body's information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:07.02,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,By renewing his body, he resets his technique\N back to the start to avoid evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.48,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:13.61,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,So becoming MetalGreymon is fine, \Nbut we can't have him evolving into SkullGreymon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:16.33,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,So we have him start over from Koromon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.75,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,What? Yeah, whatever, let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:23.83,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,The Star Plasma Vessel's location has been leaked. {you know what else has been leaked?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:28.34,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Two groups are after the young girl's life as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.13,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,One is the Curse User Group Q,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:35.64,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,which seeks to upend jujutsu society\N by having {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama} lose all reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:40.10,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,The other is the Star Religious Group\N that worships {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama},
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.85,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,known as the Time Vessel Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:48.32,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,{*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama} will assimilate the Star Plasma Vessel\N during the full moon in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:52.99,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,You are to protect the girl until then\N and ensure that she reaches {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:57.12,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,If you mess this up, the effects will ripple throughout even normal society!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:58.58,Default,Yaga,0,0,0,,Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.83,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Real talk, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:03.83,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,I kinda get why Curse User Group Q is after her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.00,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,but why would this \NStar Religious Group wanna kill the brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.88,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,What they worship is the pure form of {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:16.76,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Allowing the Star Plasma Vessel{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}in their minds,\N an impurity{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}to blend into him is simply unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.18,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,The Star Religious Group \Nis an organization of non-sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.56,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I don't think we need to worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.89,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,The ones to be wary of are Q.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.19,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.02,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,We're the strongest, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:32.19,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,That's why {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama} asked for us specifically, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.40,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:38.45,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,You know, Satoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.74,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to tell you this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.20,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,You should be more mindful of the way you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.04,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.96,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Especially when you're addressing your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:51.42,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,We might end up meeting {*}Master Tengen{*Tengen-sama}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:55.05,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,You should be more polite and humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.34,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,You'd scare your juniors less, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.01,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.59,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.81,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Come on, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.06,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.52,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,We'll discuss it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.15,Default,Kuroi,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.53,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.07,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I am, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:25.04,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Would it be our fault if the brat died from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.88,Default,Kokun,0,0,0,,Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.01,Default,Kokun,0,0,0,,If you must hate someone, hate Tengen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.26,Default,Kokun,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx180}â€”{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.31,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Could you please try not to make a scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.23,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,We got chewed out for it just this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.69,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,{\i1}This girl is the Star Plasma Vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:55.40,Default,Kokun,0,0,0,,I know that uniform.\N You're sorcerers from Jujutsu Tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.78,Default,Kokun,0,0,0,,Hand over the brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.36,Default,Kokun,0,0,0,,Or I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.53,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.78,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Come a little closer, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.08,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Man, you barely made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:11.17,Default,Bayer,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:14.17,Default,Bayer,0,0,0,,You're Gojo Satoru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.17,Default,Bayer,0,0,0,,You're famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.09,Default,Bayer,0,0,0,,I hear you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.64,Default,Bayer,0,0,0,,Let me confirm if the rumors are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:25.47,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,I'm down for that, but let's set a rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.68,Default,Bayer,0,0,0,,What rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:30.52,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,I don't wanna get yelled at for going overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:33.77,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,So if you start bawling and apologizing, I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:34.98,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,That's the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.61,Default,Bayer,0,0,0,,Cocky bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.11,Default,Kong,0,0,0,,And so it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.70,Default,Kong,0,0,0,,The Star Religious Group \Ndoesn't have the power to fight sorcerers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.79,Default,Kong,0,0,0,,But they can pay very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.41,Default,Kong,0,0,0,,That I guarantee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:50.83,Default,Kong,0,0,0,,How about it, Zenin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:55.34,Default,Kong,0,0,0,,Want to get in on the Star Plasma Vessel assassination?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.80,Default,Toji,0,0,0,,It's not Zenin anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.88,Default,Toji,0,0,0,,I took my wife's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.76,Default,Toji,0,0,0,,I go by Fushiguro now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:05.85,Default,Toji,0,0,0,,Alright, count me in.
